# Terraform local artifacts — never commit provider binaries or state.
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
# *.tfvars may hold secrets; commit *.tfvars.example instead. (Comment on its OWN line: gitignore
# has no inline comments — a trailing "# ..." becomes part of the pattern and silently matches NOTHING.)
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
# .terraform.lock.hcl IS committed once providers are pinned (Phase 3).
